WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

2
00:02:38.616 --> 00:02:40.451
{\an8}HAVE A GREAT CHUSEOK

3
00:06:25.218 --> 00:06:28.179
Yisoo. it's such an honor to meet you.

4
00:06:28.262 --> 00:06:31.724
Well. everyone has already left
for the Chuseok holiday.

5
00:06:32.475 --> 00:06:36.145
To be honest. I'd usually give this task
to a more experienced person.

6
00:06:38.439 --> 00:06:41.484
I can handle anything.
Just leave it to me.

7
00:06:45.071 --> 00:06:47.573
Koko's sitter canceled.

8
00:06:49.534 --> 00:06:51.702
But Koko has separation anxiety.

9
00:06:51.786 --> 00:06:53.246
so don't ever leave him alone.

10
00:06:53.329 --> 00:06:55.039
Keep giving him verbal affirmation.

11
00:07:05.299 --> 00:07:06.300
Do well!

12
00:07:12.598 --> 00:07:14.350
Koko. Mommy's leaving! Be good.

13
00:07:16.978 --> 00:07:19.355
What are you doing? Bring down my bag.

14
00:07:25.695 --> 00:07:26.571
Oh my God!

15
00:07:43.212 --> 00:07:44.255
You came.

16
00:07:46.757 --> 00:07:48.509
I thought of the name.

17
00:07:48.593 --> 00:07:50.845
It's mine. my brother's
and my mom's put together.

18
00:07:50.928 --> 00:07:54.515
Wow. Bora. you've grown so much!
What happened?

19
00:07:54.599 --> 00:07:55.892
Yuri! Welcome!

20
00:07:55.975 --> 00:07:58.186
Hello. Mr. Kim. Congratulations.

21
00:07:58.269 --> 00:07:59.562
Thank you.

22
00:08:00.062 --> 00:08:06.527
It's because of your family
we were able to open. I feel a little…

23
00:08:06.611 --> 00:08:08.738
Oh. there’s really no reason
to feel any way.

24
00:08:08.821 --> 00:08:10.615
- Okay.
- Excuse me.

25
00:08:10.698 --> 00:08:12.909
- Yes!
- I'll do it. Stay here and talk.

26
00:08:21.459 --> 00:08:22.710
You got a dog?

27
00:08:22.793 --> 00:08:24.212
It's my boss's.

28
00:08:24.295 --> 00:08:26.923
I had to bring him
because he can't be left alone.

29
00:08:27.006 --> 00:08:30.176
How could you bring a dog here
when we just passed a health inspection?

30
00:08:30.259 --> 00:08:31.511
We could be shut down.

31
00:08:31.594 --> 00:08:34.514
Sorry. I didn't think of that. I'll go.

32
00:08:34.597 --> 00:08:37.225
No. Dae. you can't uninvite her!

33
00:08:37.308 --> 00:08:38.601
And he's so cute!

34
00:08:38.684 --> 00:08:40.144
Don't make eye contact.

35
00:08:40.228 --> 00:08:41.187
Okay. fine.

36
00:08:41.270 --> 00:08:43.940
Just promise me
you'll keep him out of sight.

37
00:08:44.023 --> 00:08:45.816
Of course. Of course.

38
00:10:05.479 --> 00:10:07.398
Min Ho! Is Eunice coming?

39
00:10:07.481 --> 00:10:11.277
Ah. she's going to be spending
the holiday with her family.

40
00:10:36.594 --> 00:10:40.514
You wouldn't come home to me.
so I had to come to you.

41
00:10:42.683 --> 00:10:43.601
Hello.

42
00:10:43.684 --> 00:10:45.102
Yes. yes.

43
00:10:46.979 --> 00:10:48.022
Let's go.

44
00:11:34.610 --> 00:11:37.613
As a teacher. Jiwon is so popular!

45
00:11:38.656 --> 00:11:43.703
If she had stayed in Bukjeon.
she'd have been an even better teacher!

46
00:11:43.786 --> 00:11:46.247
Don't they have kids there?

47
00:11:46.330 --> 00:11:48.541
It would've been great
to have you back at home

48
00:11:48.624 --> 00:11:51.669
and see your face during the holidays.

49
00:11:51.752 --> 00:11:54.922
If I went home.
I knew you'd want me to see him.

50
00:12:21.574 --> 00:12:24.869
He's from Bukjeon.
and he has a good family.

51
00:12:24.952 --> 00:12:29.206
lots of money. and so much land!

52
00:12:49.185 --> 00:12:51.771
Halmoni.
I don't care how accomplished he is.

53
00:12:51.854 --> 00:12:54.398
Chung-Hee and I are nothing!

54
00:13:26.430 --> 00:13:29.600
I thought you'd get tired
of Seoul in a month.

55
00:13:29.683 --> 00:13:32.186
then come back home where you belong.

56
00:13:32.269 --> 00:13:36.941
I have to live my life.
not the life you want for me.

57
00:13:37.608 --> 00:13:39.151
My goodness.

58
00:13:46.700 --> 00:13:48.536
Yummy.

59
00:14:34.248 --> 00:14:36.333
Mom would be so proud of you. Dad.

60
00:14:37.501 --> 00:14:38.627
I will do my best.

61
00:14:38.711 --> 00:14:43.007
At least someone's mom
would be proud of them. Must be nice!

62
00:16:21.063 --> 00:16:22.106
Are you okay?

63
00:16:22.189 --> 00:16:24.984
No. they followed me
all the way from my parents' house.

64
00:16:25.067 --> 00:16:28.320
That was insane. I'm gonna call my dad.
tell him we need security.

65
00:16:29.488 --> 00:16:31.073
Eunice. are you okay?

66
00:16:34.201 --> 00:16:36.036
Oh my God. it's really you?

67
00:16:37.037 --> 00:16:38.789
Can I get a picture with you?

68
00:16:39.790 --> 00:16:41.333
Yeah. Of course.

69
00:17:43.062 --> 00:17:46.023
I tried to talk to my parents about it.

70
00:17:46.106 --> 00:17:47.274
but I couldn't.

71
00:17:48.650 --> 00:17:50.319
Honestly. I couldn't speak.

72
00:17:50.861 --> 00:17:53.614
I have no idea how to begin to tell them.

73
00:17:53.697 --> 00:17:56.283
I'm so scared
they'll be disappointed in me.

74
00:17:56.366 --> 00:17:58.744
What am I going to do? I'm so scared.

75
00:17:58.827 --> 00:17:59.828
No.

76
00:18:01.497 --> 00:18:02.414
Listen carefully.

77
00:18:03.457 --> 00:18:05.084
You're not alone. okay?

78
00:18:05.167 --> 00:18:07.252
I'm responsible too.

79
00:18:07.753 --> 00:18:09.338
But listen.

80
00:18:09.421 --> 00:18:11.965
You can't tell anyone about this.

81
00:18:12.049 --> 00:18:14.134
If anyone finds out. we're done!

82
00:18:15.094 --> 00:18:17.387
It's okay.

83
00:19:44.558 --> 00:19:46.018
See you back at the dorm.

84
00:26:24.749 --> 00:26:26.960
Whatever it is. you can tell me.

85
00:26:28.712 --> 00:26:31.840
Honestly. after Paris…

86
00:26:32.966 --> 00:26:34.634
I stopped having my period.

87
00:26:35.594 --> 00:26:39.556
Min Ho thinks I was with Tae-Oh.

88
00:26:39.639 --> 00:26:42.350
but obviously I was only with you.

89
00:26:45.687 --> 00:26:48.732
If you're saying
what I think you're saying.

90
00:26:50.400 --> 00:26:51.693
let's do this together.

91
00:26:52.527 --> 00:26:54.487
We can even get married if we need to.

92
00:26:55.071 --> 00:26:57.782
No. Dae. it's not like that.

93
00:26:59.367 --> 00:27:00.994
I'm not pregnant.

94
00:27:01.077 --> 00:27:02.203
Are you sure?

95
00:27:03.246 --> 00:27:09.544
For a while. I thought that I was.

96
00:27:10.211 --> 00:27:11.671
But that wasn't the case.

97
00:27:13.590 --> 00:27:16.551
When I came home tonight.

98
00:27:17.469 --> 00:27:18.970
I started my period.

99
00:27:20.513 --> 00:27:22.265
I guess I was so stressed.

100
00:27:24.476 --> 00:27:30.523
The paparazzi always following me.
fans always wanting something from me…

101
00:27:31.191 --> 00:27:34.319
Honestly. I was so scared.

102
00:27:35.779 --> 00:27:37.614
I felt like I couldn't breathe.

103
00:27:38.406 --> 00:27:40.617
Dae. I just

104
00:27:41.368 --> 00:27:45.997
want to go back
to the way things used to be.

105
00:27:46.305 --> 00:28:46.495
